    "description": "<br>为了让战争继续下去，你的角色必须活下来。 你可以通过给他们食物和饮用水来让你的角色活着。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/6a3b488acd633041c79975f53cd4b428.poster.avif?t=1725026020\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/6a3b488acd633041c79975f53cd4b428.webm?t=1725026020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/6a3b488acd633041c79975f53cd4b428.mp4?t=1725026020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>单靠军事力量不足以赢得战争 . 经济实力在战争中非常重要。 您可以通过从事毒品交易、绑架、军火走私和敲诈勒索等非法业务来为您的经济融资。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/1b0c3dcaa84f4c8221eaccb2d66545a2.poster.avif?t=1725026020\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/1b0c3dcaa84f4c8221eaccb2d66545a2.webm?t=1725026020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/1b0c3dcaa84f4c8221eaccb2d66545a2.mp4?t=1725026020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你能 让七个不同的国家共产主义？ 在你完全征服了一个你占领的国家之后，你可以开始入侵以征服一个新的国家。 记住，这对你来说很难。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/6a6d94c01bcc255a92946f01c06ec297.poster.avif?t=1725026020\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/6a6d94c01bcc255a92946f01c06ec297.webm?t=1725026020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/6a6d94c01bcc255a92946f01c06ec297.mp4?t=1725026020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>公众的幸福是最重要的。 攻下城池后，必须得民心。 记住，如果失去人民的支持，就会发生叛乱，城市将再次落入敌人手中。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/4.gif[/ img]\n战争期间你可能会陷入困境。 在这里你可以得到朋友的帮助并赢得战争。\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/46274eff32296d4ab6846aced0b04947.poster.avif?t=1725026020\" mp4=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/46274eff32296d4ab6846aced0b04947.mp4?t=1725026020\" webm=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/46274eff32296d4ab6846aced0b04947.webm?t=1725026020\" width=\"620\" height=\"350\"]\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" /></span><br>战争期间你可能会陷入困境。 在这里你可以得到朋友的帮助并赢得战争。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/46274eff32296d4ab6846aced0b04947.poster.avif?t=1725026020\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/46274eff32296d4ab6846aced0b04947.webm?t=1725026020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288300/extras/46274eff32296d4ab6846aced0b04947.mp4?t=1725026020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
